trans-unit.source: Contains the settings for the supported versions of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Enthält die Einstellungen für die unterstützten Versionen des WS-ReliableMessaging-Protokolls.

trans-unit.source: There are currently two versions of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol supported by [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)]: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 and WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005.
trans-unit.target: Es gibt derzeit zwei Versionen des WS-ReliableMessaging-Protokolls, die von [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] unterstützt werden: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 und WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005.

trans-unit.source: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 is returned by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A> and WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 is returned by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A>.
trans-unit.target: WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 wird von <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessaging11%2A> und WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 von <xref:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion.WSReliableMessagingFebruary2005%2A> zurückgegeben.

trans-unit.source: Returns the default version of WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Gibt die Standardversion des WS-ReliableMessaging-Protokolls zurück.

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> that represents the default version of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Eine von <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> abgeleitete Instanz, die die Standardversion des WS-ReliableMessaging-Protokolls darstellt.

trans-unit.source: Gets version 1.1 of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
An instance derived from <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> that represents the WS-ReliableMessaging1.1 version.
trans-unit.target: Eine von <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> abgeleitete Instanz, die die WS-ReliableMessaging1.1-Version darstellt.

trans-unit.source: Gets the February 2005 version of the WS-ReliableMessaging protocol.
trans-unit.target: Ruft die February 2005-Version des WS-ReliableMessaging-Protokolls ab.

trans-unit.source: An instance derived from <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> that represents the WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005 version.
trans-unit.target: Eine von <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.ReliableMessagingVersion" /> abgeleitete Instanz, die die WS-ReliableMessagingFebruary2005-Version darstellt.
